data.description: Step into this charming 3 bed 2 bath home in Weatherford, TX! Located in the center of Weatherford, close to the Weatherford Town Square and within walking distance of Heritage Park. You'll love the updated interior with its modern touches and spacious layout. This home also features a walk-in laundry room, spacious bedrooms, a large walk-in closet featured in the master bedroom. The kitchen features quartz countertops and GAS range. The home itself sits on generous lot, providing plenty of room for outdoor enjoyment and entertainment. Enjoy the oversized covered porch, perfect spot to relax and a great blend for comfort and space. This gem is an ideal choice for those seeking both a beautiful home and a large lot. Don't wait, Schedule a tour today!
